Why This Fix Works

Your error:

Type '{ [key: string]: string | number }' is missing properties from type 'RuleTagBackend'

Because your service returns a generic object.

This line fixes it:

const backendData = response.data as RuleTagBackend[];

Now TypeScript knows the fields exist:

TAG_CD
TAG_DESC
TAG_CAT_CD

So this mapping works safely:

tagCode: item.TAG_CD
tag: item.TAG_DESC
category: item.TAG_CAT_CD


